result.name: Le Jardin de Sophie

reviews.text: Awesome little restaurant next to the beach. Wines were amazing and we had a tasting plate of French cheese was so good. Will be back for sure. Great hosts.

Went here about a week ago after hearing about it from our friend who worked here for a few weeks, it’s a lovely place to eat, we had slow cooked steak, German sausages, the cheese board and salmon salad. The food was great and really tasty. The way the place is set up is beautiful and cosy.
Great home cooked food. Good French wine and cheese too.
Great spot for French food and wine - right on the beach with outdoor seating.
A little gem in a lost paradise of Lantau. Ideal place to eat home food and relax after a hike on the most beautiful island of HK.
